public class SecurityRestriction

setPublic

public SecurityRestriction setPublic()
Clears all current restriction entries, making the restriction accessible to anyone (public). Note this only applies to SecurityRestriction.Type.ACCESS types. Meaning EDIT types cannot be set to public.

Returns:
SecurityRestriction object with applied change
